=---
title: "The Hidden Infrastructure Costs of AI Coding Agents"
date: 2026-02-11
description: "Analysis reveals that the primary costs of running AI coding agents come from infrastructure and tooling rather than the AI models themselves, with implications for local deployment strategies."
